"""Test null packet"""
expected = (
    b'@ABCD\x00\x00\x10\x00\x00\x00\r\x00\x01\x02\x03\x04\x05\x06\x07\x08\t\n\x0b\x0c\r\x0e\x0f\x10\x11\x12\x13\x14\x15\x16\x17\x18\x19\x1a\x1b\x1c\x1d\x1e\x1f !"#$%&\'()*+,-./0123456789:;<=>?@ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ[\\]^_`abcdefghijklmn'
    )
params = dict(type='NULL', payload_length=16, number=13, none=[i for i in
    range(111)])
result = dsi.packet.build(params)
self.assertEqual(result, expected)
parsed = dsi.packet.parse(expected)
for k in params:
    self.assertEqual(parsed[k], params[k])
